Title:Incorrect calculation for negative values

Severity/Priority: High/Low

Version: 1.00

Description:There is no error display message displayed when an negative number is entered in the field.

Steps to reproduce:
1. Go to http://localhost:6464/factorial
2.Enter a negative number such as -5
3.Submit the form
4.Take note of the result

Expected result: The application should return an error message, such as that the factorial is not defined for
                negative numbers

Actual result: The application returns a message saying 'Please enter an integer'

Assigned: Josh-hf